result.name: Wheat and Wood

reviews.text: Really cool place. Definitely must visit with friends, their board games choices are insane. A plethora of options.
Huge selection of games, and a very nice drinks list. The staff are great, and so helpful!

The staff were extremely friendly and helpful! They would take take the time to explain any of the board games in a straightforward and easy-to-understand manner. 

Additionally the unique drink and food they had on offer were very inticing and delicious! Would definitely recommend to anyone, even for just a drink.

What a brilliant idea! I had so much fun at wheat and wood! There is an excellent selection of games (competitive, co-op, and giant scrabble!!), as well as a great selection of very yummy food- I highly suggest trying out the pork belly sandwich :) 

This was a perfect alternative to going out to a bar. Truly a one-of-a-kind experience. 

Thank you Wheat and Wood, I’ll be back soon!
Exactly what we were looking for, quite a few games to choose from and good beer. Wasn't busy on a Thursday night.
